TITLE: Navigating to Web Pages in CodeceptJS (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to navigate to different web pages using the amOnPage method in tests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codeceptjs/codeceptjs/blob/3.x/docs/helpers/Playwright.md#2025-04-21_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
I.amOnPage('/'); // opens main page of website
I.amOnPage('https://github.com'); // opens github
I.amOnPage('/login'); // opens a login page
```

