TITLE: Configuring Parallel Test Execution in CodeceptJS
DESCRIPTION: Configuration for running tests in parallel using multiple processes. Specifies the number of chunks (processes) and which browsers to use for all tests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codeceptjs/codeceptjs/blob/3.x/docs/changelog.md#2025-04-21_snippet_107

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
"multiple": {
  "parallel": {
    // run in 2 processes
    "chunks": 2,
    // run all tests in chrome
    "browsers": ["chrome"]
  },
}
```

