TITLE: Form Filling Test Example - Using Labels
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to interact with form elements using label text to locate fields, demonstrating filling input fields, selecting options, and submitting forms.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codeceptjs/codeceptjs/blob/3.x/docs/basics.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
I.fillField('Name', 'Miles')
I.fillField('user[email]', 'miles@davis.com')
I.selectOption('Role', 'Admin')
I.checkOption('Accept')
I.click('Save')
```

