TITLE: Sending GraphQL Mutations
DESCRIPTION: Example of sending a GraphQL mutation with variables to create a user.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codeceptjs/codeceptjs/blob/3.x/docs/helpers/GraphQL.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
I.sendMutation(`
      mutation createUser($user: UserInput!) {
         createUser(user: $user) {
           id
           name
           email
         }
       }
   `,
  { user: {
      name: 'John Doe',
      email: 'john@xmail.com'
    }
  },
});
```

