TITLE: Enabling Device Emulation in CodeceptJS with Playwright
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to enable device emulation in CodeceptJS globally using Playwright's predefined devices list. It demonstrates emulating an iPhone 6 for all tests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codeceptjs/codeceptjs/blob/3.x/docs/playwright.md#2025-04-21_snippet_16

