TITLE: Checking Input Field Values with CodeceptJS
DESCRIPTION: Uses the seeInField method to verify that a given input field or textarea equals a specific value. Fields can be located by label text, name attribute, CSS, or XPath.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codeceptjs/codeceptjs/blob/3.x/docs/helpers/WebDriver.md#2025-04-21_snippet_57

