TITLE: Mocking Network Traffic in CodeceptJS
DESCRIPTION: Intercepts and mocks network requests using Playwright's route handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codeceptjs/codeceptjs/blob/3.x/docs/helpers/Playwright.md#2025-04-21_snippet_58

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
I.mockRoute(/(.png$)|(.jpg$)/, route => route.abort());

I.mockTraffic('/api/users/1', '{ id: 1, name: \'John Doe\' }');
I.mockTraffic('/api/users/*', JSON.stringify({ id: 1, name: 'John Doe' }));
I.mockTraffic([/^https://api.example.com/v1/, 'https://api.example.com/v2/**'], 'Internal Server Error', 'text/html');
```

