TITLE: Using Grabbers in Async CodeceptJS Test
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use 'await' with grabbers like grabTitle to retrieve information from a running test and use it in assertions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codeceptjs/codeceptjs/blob/3.x/docs/basics.md#2025-04-21_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
Scenario('try grabbers', async ({ I }) => {
