TITLE: Configuring Anthropic Claude for CodeceptJS
DESCRIPTION: Configuration for using Anthropic's Claude model in CodeceptJS. This setup requires the '@anthropic-ai/sdk' package and a Claude API key set as an environment variable.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codeceptjs/codeceptjs/blob/3.x/docs/ai.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
ai: {
  request: async messages => {
    const Anthropic = require('@anthropic-ai/sdk')

    const anthropic = new Anthropic({
      apiKey: process.env.CLAUDE_API_KEY,
    })

    const resp = await anthropic.messages.create({
      model: 'claude-2.1',
      max_tokens: 1024,
      messages,
    })
    return resp.content.map(c => c.text).join('\n\n')
  }
}
```

